00:30:38,687 --> 00:30:41,771
Why in God's name
would you do that?

488
00:30:45,494 --> 00:30:47,059
I was trying to help.

489
00:30:48,196 --> 00:30:50,297
She didn't wanna come.

490
00:30:50,399 --> 00:30:52,719
