yourself, not me.

492
00:30:56,821 --> 00:30:59,189
Yourself.

493
00:31:00,125 --> 00:31:02,359
I hit the ring in the woods.

494
00:31:02,461 --> 00:31:03,910
In the woods.

495
00:31:06,265 --> 00:31:07,497
You destroyed me.

496
00:31:16,675 --> 00:31:20,226
This is the final dissection.
