497
00:31:20,329 --> 00:31:23,129
I'll connect vessels and nerves.
Get the microscope ready.

498
00:31:23,231 --> 00:31:25,315
Yes, right away.

499
00:31:27,519 --> 00:31:29,569
OK, people. It's time.

500
00:31:31,140 --> 00:31:34,224
