00:35:07,989 --> 00:35:11,591
but I need you to tell
me that it's gonna be OK.

551
00:35:11,693 --> 00:35:14,177
You're my surgeon, after all.

552
00:35:16,281 --> 00:35:18,881
This isn't a silly procedure
to me, Miss Sulley.

553
00:35:18,983 --> 00:35:22,718
- And I will get you
through this.
- OK.

554
00:35:22,821 --> 00:35:24,220
Thank you.

555
00:35:25,640 --> 00:35:26,989
I'm ready now.

556
00:35:46,445 --> 00:35:48,911
Izzie has stage four
metastatic melanoma

557
00:35:49,014 --> 00:35:51,547
