her brain, liver and skin.

558
00:35:51,649 --> 00:35:55,935
She may only have months to
live and she's resisting treatment.

559
00:35:56,037 --> 00:35:58,004
She needs help.

560
00:36:02,294 --> 00:36:03,826
Scalpel.

561
00:36:04,996 --> 00:36:08,498
<i>♪ Look, it's a mirror
