567
00:36:31,323 --> 00:36:35,658
But yeah. I'll give
you a sneak peak.

568
00:37:28,196 --> 00:37:30,630
Sometimes we fail, but
that's not always the case.

569
00:37:30,732 --> 00:37:32,665
I know.

570
00:37:32,767 --> 00:37:34,434
Blowhole has a new face.

