580
00:38:10,438 --> 00:38:11,921
Thank you.

581
00:38:51,012 --> 00:38:52,479
Dr. Grey.

582
00:38:53,648 --> 00:38:55,460
They think you're
taking advantage of me,

583
00:38:55,484 --> 00:38:56,782
